@dpgaspar the structure looks ok to me as is, my original idea was to just made EVENT_LOGGER a simple function, but the abstraction you have is more modular I guess

It could be good to allow us to shut down the current Log model and ModelView, but these really don't hurt. Main goal here is a hook to allow for hijacking / rewiring these events.

Another PR could add decorate many more views with @logthis

